      <title>欧洲央行称欧洲银行仍低估气候风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecb-says-european-banks-are-still-under-estimating-climate-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最高监管机构表示，欧洲银行正在将气候风险纳入其发放的抵押贷款条款中，尽管它们尚未完全了解潜在成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecb-says-european-banks-are-still-under-estimating-climate-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 09:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行加入看跌行列，看跌陷入困境的奢侈品行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/bofa-joins-growing-bearish-chorus-on-troubled-luxury-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲奢侈品股进一步下跌，美国银行分析师成为最新一家对陷入困境的奢侈品行业发出警报的分析师，他们将行业领头羊路威酩轩集团的评级下调至中性，并下调了其他公司的评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/bofa-joins-growing-bearish-chorus-on-troubled-luxury-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:56:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司事件后，修复英国污水泄漏的成本将更高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/thames-water-s-mess-is-going-to-make-fixing-leaky-uk-more-costly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果以最近的债券销售情况作为参考，泰晤士水务公司的困境将使英国水务行业付出沉重代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/thames-water-s-mess-is-going-to-make-fixing-leaky-uk-more-costly</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:40:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利预算因 Meloni 下调 2023 年债务而增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/meloni-gets-italian-budget-boost-with-2023-debt-revised-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利数据经过多年修订后，其债务比率降低了近三个百分点，这为意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼政府在准备公布新的预算目标时提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/meloni-gets-italian-budget-boost-with-2023-debt-revised-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:38:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者消化新内阁 法债市场风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/france-s-yield-premium-over-germany-rises-to-most-since-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶（Michel Barnier）新内阁所面临的挑战及其控制国家巨额赤字的能力，法国政府债券表现落后于其他债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/france-s-yield-premium-over-germany-rises-to-most-since-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场押注欧洲央行加快降息，德国收益率曲线趋于正常化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/german-bond-yield-curve-normalizes-for-first-time-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商押注欧洲央行将需要加快降息步伐，且人们越来越担心该地区经济复苏已经失去动力，德国收益率曲线的一个关键部分已经正常化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/german-bond-yield-curve-normalizes-for-first-time-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:12:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区私营部门因制造业衰退而再次萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/euro-zone-private-sector-back-in-contraction-on-factory-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着法国奥运经济刺激政策的结束和制造业衰退的加剧，欧元区私营部门经济出现自 3 月份以来的首次萎缩，人们担心该地区经济复苏势头已经丧失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/euro-zone-private-sector-back-in-contraction-on-factory-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者对增长前景持谨慎态度，防御性股票推动欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/european-stocks-muted-as-commerzbank-drops-on-deal-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡地区经济增长放缓迹象与全球经济复苏预期，欧洲股市在防御性股票上涨的推动下小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/european-stocks-muted-as-commerzbank-drops-on-deal-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价创下 4 月以来最大周涨幅后企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强抵消了人们对以色列和真主党之间的冲突可能演变为地区战争的担忧，油价在创下 4 月份以来最大单周涨幅后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 23:32:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rightmove 将考虑 REA 集团新的 61 亿英镑收购报价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/murdoch-s-rea-sweetens-bid-again-for-rightmove-to-6-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Rightmove Plc 表示，将考虑 REA Group Ltd. 提出的 61 亿英镑（81 亿美元）的加价报价，这是该澳大利亚房地产门户网站在不到三周内提出的第三项报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/murdoch-s-rea-sweetens-bid-again-for-rightmove-to-6-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 23:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
